\sigma
\{1,2,\dots,n\}
\text{Fix}(\sigma) = \{ 1 \leq i \leq n : \sigma(i) = i \}
 \sum_{\sigma \in S_n} |\text{Fix}(\sigma)| = \sum_{\sigma \in S_n} \sum_{i \in \text{Fix}(\sigma)} 1. 
 \sum_{i=1}^n \sum_{\sigma \in S_n : \sigma(i) = i} 1 = \sum_{i=1}^n (n-1)! = n \cdot (n-1)! = n!. 
